KeepAlive yes
ServerAliveInterval 60

Host                github.com
    User            git
    Hostname        ssh.github.com
    IdentityFile    ~/.ssh/id_rsa
    IdentitiesOnly  yes
    Port            443

Host                bitbucket.org
    User            git
    Hostname        altssh.bitbucket.org
    IdentityFile    ~/.ssh/id_rsa
    IdentitiesOnly  yes
    Port            443
